{"tid":2367252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《處境題》假設有一日漂流荒島的你.....","createTime":"2021-01-15T07:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T10:50:35.000Z","uid":389183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54832f7115ae49ac6de11ceba150174f319310dc","tid":2367252,"uid":389183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T07:50:05.000Z","msg":"有日你出海不幸地碰上風暴，遊艇沉左，而你就大難不死抱住浮木飄浮荒島。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><ins>島的描述</ins></span><br />\n島上面有食人族<br />\n有野生動物<br />\n有隻破船<br />\n有好多果實，但有幾種有劇毒<br />\n夜晚島氣溫會急降至2-3度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候你最需要邊三件<span class=\"red\">工具或物件</span>，令你可以係荒島生存落去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">係工具或物件 係工具或物件 係工具物件</span></span>因為好重要重複三次<br />\n唔好同我講要女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04fe182e2837e901913b45dc4dfcb0c3ccd428a","tid":2367252,"uid":7093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T07:57:10.000Z","msg":"船同GPS"},{"pid":"6709986aef5d1a4f07fa3a4c4f836e7677fbcd1b","tid":2367252,"uid":389183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b04fe182e2837e901913b45dc4dfcb0c3ccd428a","tid":2367252,"uid":7093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T07:57:10.000Z","msg":"船同GPS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔俾出海 要焗住係個荒島生存"},{"pid":"c30dc8e5fa46b7fc95d077a231d0eda3145ed83d","tid":2367252,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T08:04:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G8Z5r3y7l3k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG8Z5r3y7l3k&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=fbe564ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G8Z5r3y7l3k</a>"},{"pid":"e3d0807c8e8ef5506d466057bd1b3f3b7795ed50","tid":23